Item details
Highlights
Made by WoodAndMine
Materials: Wood
A beautiful, bamboo coaster set of 4 lovingly engraved with the initials and / text / names / date of your choice. They’re perfect for a wedding, housewarming, anniversary, or any special occasion needing a personal, chic, and creative touch. (I personally love them for wedding favors!) ♡

Each coaster will be custom engraved to the text you specify at checkout: Initial(s) for the center with the wording of your choice for the circle.

► 10cm x 10cm x .8cm

► Handmade in the USA with sustainable, reclaimed bamboo

► Sold in sets of 4 or 8

► Arrives neatly tied with raffia

► Complimentary gift note included upon request

► Quantity discounts available, please message me for more information

► Handmade with solid, sustainable, naturally antimicrobial bamboo

♡♡ For the matching cutting board + coasters + serving spoon gift set, click here:


<><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><>
<><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><>

► To view the entire Wood be Mine collection and find the perfect gift for you and yours, visit my shop home page:

► Wood Be Mine is a woman-owned and operated home business. I personally review, create, pack and ship each order right from my studio! Every order is hand crafted with quality materials and attention to detail, ensuring each piece is a lasting, meaningful gift.

<><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><>
<><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><>

► ORDERING:
To order your custom engraved product, simply add the item to your cart and proceed to the check out. Enter your personalization info and desired text in the “Note to seller” comment box during payment. Please note that any and all text / wording in my designs can be personalized.

If requesting a gift note, enter your desired message here. Please specify if you would like to receive a proof through Etsy before your item is engraved and above all... be sure to proofread!

► TURNAROUND & SHIPPING:
My processing time varies seasonally. For current order turnaround, please check the FAQ by scrolling to the bottom of this listing. If you request a proof, you will receive an image of your custom design via Etsy Conversations 24 - 48 hours before your order is due to be shipped. Once you give me the A-OK, your product will be engraved and shipped via USPS or Fedex, depending on destination, in the order it was received.

> > > Need it sooner? I have several rush production options available here:
(Link may be inactive during high season!)

► CUSTOM ORDERS:
I love designing new and unique pieces! If you have some ideas for a design that you not see in my shop, please contact me and I would be happy to work with you to create a gift that’s yours and yours alone :) Additionally, if you already have a design or image of your own that you would like engraved, (wedding invite, logo, etc.,) Please contact me to discuss pricing / placement.

Special care and attention is given to each handmade product, made in my home based studio in Oregon, USA.

► A COMMITMENT TO GOING GREEN: ♡ ♡ ♡
Wood Be Mine's products, practices, AND packaging are eco-friendly. May you have no fear of receiving your sustainable product wrapped in plastic or packed with styrofoam peanuts. Only compostable or recyclable materials are used in every step of my process!
